            <genre>Fantasy</genre>
        </information>

        <description>
            <short>
                A vaguely humanoid shape made of earth. Summoned
                with Fyvrian magic.
            </short>

            <physical>
                <para>
                    An earth elemental looks like a misshapen human,
                    with bulky muscles and an almost featureless head.
                    It is made of soft earth, often with grass or
                    other plants growing out of it.
                </para>

                <para>
                    Earth elementals grow in physical size and strength
                    according to their type rank. For every rank it has,
                    an earth elemental has three points of size and strength,
                    five points of soak.
                </para>

                <table>
                    <thead>
