                            <entry>Dmg</entry>
                        </row>
                    </thead>

                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry>I</entry><entry>3 (Small)</entry><entry>3</entry><entry>8</entry>
                            <entry>+0</entry><entry>+0</entry><entry>+0</entry><entry>+0</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>II</entry><entry>6 (Medium)</entry><entry>6/5</entry><entry>12</entry>
                            <entry>+0</entry><entry>+0</entry><entry>+0</entry><entry>+0</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>III</entry><entry>9 (Large)</entry><entry>9/7</entry><entry>16</entry>
                            <entry>+2</entry><entry>+3</entry><entry>+2</entry><entry>+0</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>IV</entry><entry>12 (Huge)</entry><entry>12/8</entry><entry>20</entry>
                            <entry>+5</entry><entry>+6</entry><entry>+4</entry><entry>+0</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>V</entry><entry>15 (Huge)</entry><entry>15/9</entry><entry>24</entry>
                            <entry>+5</entry><entry>+6</entry><entry>+4</entry><entry>+0</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>VI</entry><entry>18 (Enormous)</entry><entry>18/10</entry><entry>28</entry>
                            <entry>+10</entry><entry>+9</entry><entry>+6</entry><entry>+0</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>VII</entry><entry>21 (Enormous)</entry><entry>21/11</entry><entry>32</entry>
                            <entry>+10</entry><entry>+9</entry><entry>+6</entry><entry>+0</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>VIII</entry><entry>24 (Gigantic)</entry><entry>24/12</entry><entry>36</entry>
                            <entry>+15</entry><entry>+12</entry><entry>+8</entry><entry>+0</entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>

                </table>

                <para>
                    Earth elementals of huge size loose their humanoid
                    appearance, and take on a three legged, dome like,
                    body structure, spreading outwards, but not really
                    exceeding 5m in height.
                </para>

                <para>
                    Enormous and gigantic earth elementals are four
                    legged creatures, trading bulk and width for height
                    and length. Nevertheless, a type VIII earth elemental
                    is over 15m in length and about 7m tall.
                </para>
            </physical>

            <tactics>
                <para>
                    An earth elemental has a brawl skill equal to its
                    rank + 2.
                </para>
            </tactics>
        </description>

