                    All edged attacks do only stun damage to a water elemental,
                    and piercing attacks are ignored.
                </para>
            </tactics>

            <powers>
                <para>
                    If a water elemental is in contact with a body of water
                    at least ten times the mass of the elemental, then it can
                    regenerate any damage at a rate of one wound or stun a
                    round. If the elemental is half submerged, then it
                    regenerates at double rate, and if fully submerged, then
                    it regenerates at triple rate.
                </para>
